### Generate storyboard
POST http://localhost:7071/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/storyboard
Idempotency-Key: {{guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"scenesHint":["Hook","Value","CTA"],"maxScenes":6}

### Get storyboard
GET http://localhost:7071/v1/storyboards/{{storyboardId}}

### Create render
POST http://localhost:7071/v1/renders
Idempotency-Key: {{guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"projectId":"{{projectId}}","storyboardId":"{{storyboardId}}","quality":"hd","codec":"h264","notifyWebhook":"https://example.com/webhook"}

### Get render
GET http://localhost:7071/v1/renders/{{renderId}}

### Cancel render
POST http://localhost:7071/v1/renders/{{renderId}}/cancel

### Webhooks
POST http://localhost:7071/v1/webhooks
Content-Type: application/json

{"url":"https://example.com/hook","secret":"<generate-32-bytes>","events":["render.completed","render.failed"]}

